Topps Finest x Topps Total Football Terms
Last Updated: 305d
Welcome to the Topps Finest x Topps Total Football Program. By participating in this Program, you agree to these terms. Please read them carefully. Topps may amend or modify these terms from time to time in its discretion.
Unless additionally stated below, terms of Topps Total Football apply to this promotion. These can be found here:
https://total-football.helpshift.com/hc/en/3-topps-total-football/faq/19-topps-total-football-terms-of-use/
The privacy policy of Topps Total Football also applies to this promotion, this can be found here:
https://total-football.helpshift.com/hc/en/3-topps-total-football/faq/18-topps-total-football-privacy-policy/
What is the activation?
Within some packs of the new 2023/24 UEFA Topps Finest product, there are "Total Football's Finest" cards, that have a Topps Total Football x Topps Finest logo on the front and a scratch-off code on the reverse. Once scratched off, a code is revealed that can be entered into the Topps Total Football app. This code will deliver a digital parallel of a Total Football's Finest card. A physical copy of this parallel card can then be subsequently printed using the Topps Total Football application functionality at the cost stiuplated within the app.
When does this program begin and end?
The program begins at the official Topps Finest release date of May 15, 2024. The program ends on December 31, 2024 at 11:59GMT. Codes cannot be redeemed after this time, but any claimed cards within the app can be printed until August 31, 2025 at 11:59GMT.
The Program is offered at Toppsâ€™ sole discretion. We may, in our discretion, cancel, amend, modify, restrict, and/or terminate these Program Terms and/or the Program, or any aspect or feature of the Program, at any time without prior notice.
How do I redeem the code?
Step 1:
If you don't have the app already, download the Topps Total Football app from the Apple App Store or Google Play store here:
https://topps.sng.link/Dtrip/6k27p?_smtype=3
Step 2:
Create a new account or link to an existing Topps Total Football account. Complete the tutorial if you have not done so already.
Step 3:
Click the settings icon in the top corner of the home page.
Step 4:
Select "Redeem" from the menu that appears.
Step 5:
Enter the code seen on the back of your card. This is case-sensitive. A sequence will play and your card will be awarded. This can then be used in the app for trading, printing or viewing.
What if I canâ€™t read the unlock code?
If the unlock code cannot be read, please hand print your information on the back of the redemption card and mail it to:
Topps Europe Limited,
REF: Topps Total Football,
PO Box 850,
Milton Keynes,
MK8 0HU,
UK.
Cards containing the code will not be returned.
What happens if Topps cannot read the code once it is mailed in?
If Topps is unable to read the code printed on the unlock card, the card will not be redeemed. The card is void.
What happens if the system says my code is invalid?
Please reach out to our support team via the in-app settings menu or here:
https://total-football.helpshift.com/hc/en/3-topps-total-football/contact-us/
How many times can an unlock code be redeemed?
Unlock codes can only be redeemed one time. Any additional attempts to redeem a code will be rejected and the unlock code will be void.
When do I have to enter my unlock code?
Unlock codes must be received or entered within Topps Total Football no later than the expiration date printed on the unlock card. Expiration dates cannot be extended. Please make sure to review the expiration date on the back of the unlock card.
How do I submit an expired unlock code?
Once an unlock code expires, it cannot be extended or redeemed.
How do I contact Topps about this program?
Please reach out to our support team via the in-app settings menu or here:
https://total-football.helpshift.com/hc/en/3-topps-total-football/contact-us/
